// Known current bug - "trackers-detected" tabs don't always remember that they should show "trackers-detected" panels.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Go to CNN, click icon (See the "trakcers-detected" panel).
2. Open new tab, go to about:debugging, click icon and see the "no-trackers" panel.
3. Go back to CNN tab and click the icon - It's now forgotten (perhaps because it's done blocking reqs?) that it should show a "trackers-detected" panel on icon click.

